about us
our commitment to the Irish experience
paddy mac’s has been proudly serving warm service, premium drinks and authentic Irish cuisine to
palm beach county for over 25 years
Hugh Jackson
PROPRIETOR
Born in Cork City, Ireland, Hugh has spent years in the food and beverage industry throughout Ireland, London, and America. Some of his favorite experiences include working at Youngs Brewery and Fast Eddies. After coming to the U.S. and spending a short stint in construction, Hugh discovered Paddy Mac’s in 1996. Hugh worked his way up from bartender to partner in 2013 and then became the owner in 2015, sole proprietor in 2019. He has continued his commitment towards warm service, premium drinks and authentic Irish cuisine for Paddy Mac’s ever since. Hugh describes his time at Paddy Mac’s as “the American dream.”
